high_descs: Walk forward until you reach the shower then take a right stopping at the trashcan.
Take the soap out of the trash can.
Put the soap in the tub to the right of the drain.
Put the soap in the tub to the right of the drain.
Turn right for one step, turn left and take six steps and stop at the toilet.
Pick up the pink bar of soap from the top of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk six steps, turn right for one step, turn right again.
Put the soap, facing left and right, to the left of the soap already in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of pink soap in the bathtub near the drain.

high_descs: Turn right and face the trash bin
Pick up the soap in the trash bine
Turn left then head to the tub
Put the soap in the tub
Walk toward the toilet tank
Pick up the soap on the tank
Turn right then head to the tub
Put the soap in the tub beside the other soap
anns.task_desc: Put the two soap in the tub

high_descs: Move to the bucket between the sink and the shower.
Pick up the bar of soap out of the bucket.
Turn around and go to the corner of the bathtub on the the other end of the sink.
Place the bar of soap on the side of the bathtub.
Move straight across the room to the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap off the left end side of the toilet top behind the candle.
Turn around and go back to the corner of the bathtub next to the sink.
Place the bar of soap down inside the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Take two bars of soap to the bathtub.
